[i](As this enters, insert it into one of your three programs.)[/i]
[i]Corrupt[/i] – When this Subroutine enters while you control a permanent with greater mana value, it runs.
Whenever this Subroutine runs, create two 1/1 white Citizen creature tokens. They gain haste until end of turn.
